{"tid":1607780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警犬派人去\"外國勢力\"受訓","createTime":"2019-10-01T04:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T00:13:41.000Z","uid":328351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"79476f8e890f1c76026bedd753ed16b9b7989a4d","tid":1607780,"uid":328351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"黑警最叻話自己點專業，喺網上&quot;警聲&quot; ([url]Offbeat - <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/archives_2013_c.htm[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2Farchives_2013_c.htm%5B%2Furl%5D&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=56f01456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/archives_2013_c.htm[/url]</a>) 有相有名登哂派左D人去澳洲，美國，英國etc上堂，學leadership, management, conflict resolution, and police ethics. 學成返嚟就升官發財，好多個喺呢幾個月出哂名有份搞嘢。例如，<br />\n<br />\n方志堅 - Australian Institute of Police Management<br />\n吳樂俊，梁子健，周一鳴，何啟軒 - Harvard Kennedy School<br />\n高振邦 - London School of Economics<br />\n<br />\nCharles Sturt University (澳洲) 同Cambridge 都同警犬有joint program 俾碩士位 (<a href=\"https://www.crim.cam.ac.uk/mst-documents/hong-kong-course-dates-2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crim.cam.ac.uk%2Fmst-documents%2Fhong-kong-course-dates-2019&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=b32ea4a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.crim.cam.ac.uk/mst-documents/hong-kong-course-dates-2019</a>) (<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1117/eng/6985.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1117%2Feng%2F6985.html&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=4839f5b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1117/eng/6985.html</a>).<br />\n<br />\nOxford 都有program 俾警犬讀。<br />\n<br />\n一句講哂，嘥納税人錢俾佢升職做賤格濫權衰嘢。D學校應該同警犬割蓆唔好legitimize呢個政權，唔好俾佢地利用去增加聲譽。我己經喺twitter出咗post俾呢D學校。如果覺得有用唔該retweet. (#hongkongprotests #standwithhongkong)<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他 e.g. Queensland Police Service Academy, Victoria Police Academy, University of California, Berkeley, Scottish Police College, Canadian Police College, and International Police Association. 我會再post勸佢哋割蓆。<br />\n<br />\n整咗個database收集咗警犬去&quot;外國勢力&quot;受訓D資料。唔知有冇用。"},{"pid":"f033090ebf3219b4d461b45895493397e242d782","tid":1607780,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"有冇backup, 死晒link"},{"pid":"2c909b80e9c41f2d1acf8196838caf187ce5c2c4","tid":1607780,"uid":328351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"警聲主頁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/archives_2013_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2Farchives_2013_c.htm&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=09942065\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/archives_2013_c.htm</a> <br />\nCambridge program (PDF document):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.crim.cam.ac.uk/mst-documents/hong-kong-course-dates-2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crim.cam.ac.uk%2Fmst-documents%2Fhong-kong-course-dates-2019&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=b32ea4a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.crim.cam.ac.uk/mst-documents/hong-kong-course-dates-2019</a><br />\nCharles Sturt University program:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1117/eng/6985.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1117%2Feng%2F6985.html&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdbtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=4839f5b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1117/eng/6985.html</a>"},{"pid":"5be4cf1e81ed8c7b6b23799f172ac9ab0eb05a23","tid":1607780,"uid":328351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:13:41.000Z","msg":"知唔知呢班人有冇份參與清場行動? 納税人俾錢佢哋去UC Berkeley讀executive management <img src=\